query:
UPDATE 
            nats_trigger
        SET
            nats_resource_path = $1,
            subjects = $2,
            stream_name = $3,
            consumer_name = $4,
            use_jetstream = $5,
            script_path = $6,
            path = $7,
            is_flow = $8,
            edited_by = $9,
            email = $10,
            edited_at = now(),
            server_id = NULL,
            error = NULL,
            error_handler_path = $13,
            error_handler_args = $14,
            retry = $15
        WHERE
            workspace_id = $11 AND path = $12
